    <h2>
      <a href="/episodes/133-capistrano-tasks-revised">Capistrano Tasks (revised)</a>
      
    </h2>
    <div class="description">
      Learn the basics of writing Capistrano tasks, how to set variables, and run commands on a remote server. Then peak into the internals of Capistrano&#x27;s deploy tasks to see how they work.
      <span class="stats">(10 minutes)</span>
    </div>
