    <h2>
      <a href="/episodes/201-bundler-revised">Bundler (revised)</a>
      
    </h2>
    <div class="description">
      Bundler makes it easy to manage Ruby Gem dependencies. Learn how to use it in a Rails application, see what&#x27;s new in Bundler 1.1, convenient ways to run bundle exec, and how to fix gem compilation issues.
      <span class="stats">(9 minutes)</span>
